---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Star, CheckCircle, XCircle, MessageCircle, Video, Phone, Clock } from 'lucide-react';

const platforms = [];
---

<BaseLayout>
<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        {/* Hero Section */}
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Online Therapy Communication Features Compared</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            How therapy platforms handle messaging, live sessions, and therapist availability
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Introduction Section */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">The Importance of Communication in Online Therapy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Communication is the foundation of effective therapy. In the online therapy world, platforms offer various ways to connect with therapistsâ€”from asynchronous messaging to live video sessions. The communication methods available, their quality, and the responsiveness of therapists can significantly impact your therapeutic experience.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Different communication styles suit different needs. Some clients benefit from the reflection time that messaging provides, while others need the immediacy and personal connection of video sessions. Many find that a combination of approaches works best, allowing for both ongoing support and deeper therapeutic work.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            In this guide, we evaluate the communication features of leading online therapy platforms, comparing their messaging capabilities, live session quality, and therapist responsiveness to help you find the best fit for your communication preferences.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Communication Methods Comparison */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Understanding Different Communication Methods</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-10">
            {communicationMethods.map((method, index) => (
              <div key={index} class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-8 last:border-0 last:pb-0">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                  {method.icon}
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 ml-3">{method.method}</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">{method.description}</p>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
                      <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2" />
                      Benefits
                    </h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                      {method.benefits.map((benefit, i) => (
                        <li key={i} class="flex items-start">
                          <CheckCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
                          <span class="text-gray-600">{benefit}</span>
                        </li>
                      ))}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
                      <XCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2" />
                      Limitations
                    </h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                      {method.limitations.map((limitation, i) => (
                        <li key={i} class="flex items-start">
                          <XCircle class="h-4 w-4 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" />
                          <span class="text-gray-600">{limitation}</span>
                        </li>
                      ))}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-4">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-1">Best For</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">{method.bestFor}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Platform Comparison Table */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12 overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Communication Features by Platform</h2>
          
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="min-w-full min-w-0 divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Platform</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Messaging</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Live Sessions</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Response Time</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Overall</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
                {platforms.map((platform) => (
                  <tr key={platform.slug}>
                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">
                      <div class="font-medium text-gray-900">{platform.name}</div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">
                      <div class="flex items-center">
                        {renderStars(platform.messagingRating)}
                        <span class="ml-2 text-gray-600">{platform.messagingRating}</span>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">
                      <div class="flex items-center">
                        {renderStars(platform.liveSessionsRating)}
                        <span class="ml-2 text-gray-600">{platform.liveSessionsRating}</span>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">
                      <div class="flex items-center">
                        {renderStars(platform.responseTimeRating)}
                        <span class="ml-2 text-gray-600">{platform.responseTimeRating}</span>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap">
                      <div class="flex items-center">
                        {renderStars(platform.overallRating)}
                        <span class="ml-2 text-gray-600">{platform.overallRating}</span>
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Detailed Platform Reviews */}
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Detailed Communication Analysis by Platform</h2>

          {platforms.map((platform, index) => (
            <div key={platform.slug} class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden mb-8">
              <div class="p-8">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
                  <div class="md:w-1/4 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
                      <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600 mr-3">{index + 1}</span>
                      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">{platform.name}</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                      <div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
                          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Messaging</span>
                          <div class="flex">
                            {renderStars(platform.messagingRating)}
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
                          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Live Sessions</span>
                          <div class="flex">
                            {renderStars(platform.liveSessionsRating)}
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
                          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Response Time</span>
                          <div class="flex">
                            {renderStars(platform.responseTimeRating)}
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="pt-2 border-t border-gray-200">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1">
                          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-700">Overall</span>
                          <div class="flex">
                            {renderStars(platform.overallRating)}
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                      <button class="w-full min-w-0 justify-center">Full Review</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="md:w-3/4 md:pl-8">
                    <div class="mb-6">
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
                        <MessageCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                        Messaging Features
                      </h4>
                      <ul class="space-y-2">
                        {platform.messagingFeatures.map((feature, i) => (
                          <li key={i} class="flex items-start">
                            <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                            <span class="text-gray-600">{feature}</span>
                          </li>
                        ))}
                      </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
                        <Video class="h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600 mr-2" />
                        Live Session Features
                      </h4>
                      <ul class="space-y-2">
                        {platform.liveSessionFeatures.map((feature, i) => (
                          <li key={i} class="flex items-start">
                            <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                            <span class="text-gray-600">{feature}</span>
                          </li>
                        ))}
                      </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                      <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Communication Pros</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2">
                          {platform.pros.map((pro, i) => (
                            <li key={i} class="flex items-start">
                              <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                              <span class="text-gray-600">{pro}</span>
                            </li>
                          ))}
                        </ul>
                      </div>

                      <div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Communication Cons</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2">
                          {platform.cons.map((con, i) => (
                            <li key={i} class="flex items-start">
                              <XCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                              <span class="text-gray-600">{con}</span>
                            </li>
                          ))}
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        {/* Communication Preferences Section */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Finding Your Communication Fit</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">For Those Who Value Ongoing Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                If you benefit from consistent support and like processing thoughts throughout the week, prioritize platforms with strong messaging features:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Best options:</strong> BetterHelp, Talkspace</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Look for:</strong> Unlimited messaging, quick response times, multiple messaging formats</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Avoid:</strong> Platforms with session-only models or limited messaging</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">For Those Who Prefer Face-to-Face Interaction</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                If you value nonverbal cues and real-time conversation, prioritize platforms with excellent live session capabilities:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Best options:</strong> Amwell, Online-Therapy.com</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Look for:</strong> High-quality video, flexible session scheduling, longer session times</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Avoid:</strong> Platforms that limit live sessions or charge significant extra fees for them</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">For Those Who Want a Balanced Approach</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                If you value both ongoing messaging support and regular live sessions, look for platforms that excel in both areas:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Best options:</strong> Calmerry, BetterHelp</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Look for:</strong> Plans that include both messaging and weekly sessions as standard</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Avoid:</strong> Platforms that excel in one communication type but are weak in others</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">For Those With Privacy Concerns</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
                If you have limited privacy at home or prefer more discreet therapy options:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Best options:</strong> Platforms with text-based options like BetterHelp (live chat) or Talkspace (messaging)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Look for:</strong> Phone session options, live chat capabilities, discreet app interfaces</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-gray-600"><strong>Avoid:</strong> Platforms without text-based options or those requiring video/audio</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Conclusion */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Recommendations</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Based on our comprehensive analysis of communication features across online therapy platforms, here are our top recommendations:
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Best Overall Communication Features: BetterHelp</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                BetterHelp offers the most comprehensive and flexible communication options, with unlimited messaging in multiple formats (text, audio, video) and weekly live sessions via video, phone, or live chat. Their platform provides the best balance of asynchronous and synchronous communication methods.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Best for Structured Communication: Talkspace</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Talkspace excels with its organized messaging system and guaranteed response timeframes. Their structured approach to asynchronous therapy makes it ideal for those who appreciate clear communication boundaries and consistent therapist engagement.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Best Video Session Quality: Amwell</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                For those who prioritize high-quality video sessions similar to traditional therapy, Amwell offers the most professional telehealth experience. Their video platform is reliable, and their 45-minute sessions provide ample time for meaningful therapeutic work.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Best Value for Communication Features: Calmerry</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Calmerry provides a good balance of messaging and video sessions at a more affordable price point than some competitors. Their platform offers consistent response times and reliable video quality without premium pricing.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-6">
            When choosing an online therapy platform, consider your personal communication preferences, therapy goals, and practical constraints like privacy and internet access. The right communication methods can significantly enhance your therapeutic experience and outcomes.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* CTA Section */}
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-lg p-8 text-white text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Find Your Perfect Communication Style</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Take our assessment to get matched with the online therapy platform that best fits your communication preferences and needs.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/tools/matchers/therapy-platform-matcher" class="inline-flex items-center bg-indigo-600 text-white px-6 py-3 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition">Take the Assessment</a>
            <a href="/compare/platforms/top-therapy-platforms-compared" class="border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:bg-opacity-10">Compare All Platforms</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
